   - `--k_test`: number of testing data instances to generate, default is '1000'.
   - `--m`: number of constraints in each LP instance, default is '10'.
   - `--n`: number of variables in each LP instance, default is '50'.
   - `--nnz`: number of nonzero elements in the matrix A of each LP instance, default is '100'.
   - `--prob`: probability that a constraint is an equality constraint, default is '0.3'.

